544
00:37:30,823 --> 00:37:33,758
Entre, entre.
Por favor, sente-se.

545
00:37:37,530 --> 00:37:39,898
Olá, é o Jeff Clarke, certo?

546
00:37:39,899 --> 00:37:41,266
Sim, senhora.

547
00:37:41,267 --> 00:37:43,535
